</li>
<li><strong>Lüks Seçenek:</strong> <strong>Grand Hotel Les Trois Rois</strong> (<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Grand&#43;Hotel&#43;Les&#43;Trois&#43;Rois&#43;Basel"  target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Google Maps</a> | <a href="https://www.booking.com/search.html?ss=Grand&#43;Hotel&#43;Les&#43;Trois&#43;Rois&#43;Basel"  target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Booking.com</a>)
